              "type": "text",
              "text": "An open access keyboard and its containing app can send keystroke data to your server, which enables you to apply your computing resources to features like touch-event processing and input prediction. If you employ this capability, do not store received keystroke or voice data beyond the time needed to provide text back to the user or to provide features that you explain to the user. "
